      "span_text": "Following international guidelines, [CITATION_1] patients with HCV genotypes 1 or 4 received either 48 or 72 weeks of treatment, and patients with HCV genotype 3 received 24 or 48 weeks of treatment, in accordance with the decision of the physician responsible for the patient."
